lapse. like you suggested.</i>

208
00:21:31.013 --> 00:21:34.465
<i>but so far.
all I've captured are orbs.</i>

209
00:21:34.569 --> 00:21:36.467
<i>I'd have thought
an old house like this</i>

210
00:21:36.571 --> 00:21:38.100
